'''Mark Tedin''' is an artist who first began working for [[Wizards of the Coast]] over eighteen years ago. His most notable work is for the collectible card game Magic, but he has also illustrated for a number of their ''Star Wars'' products.

Tedin has occasionally edited [[Wookieepedia]] under the username {{U|Bantha68}}.

